title: Kintore Joshi to Ecchi na Micchaku Training Shichaimashita
description:
You’ve seen anthologies of manga about girls with big boobs, manga about girls falling in love with guys, and even manga about girls falling in love with each other. Now it’s time to get ready for the next level: an anthology of manga about cute girls exercising.

Cover by Tsuji Santa
1. Somehow, Morimoto san is very Trusting by SAKURA Hanatsumi
2. Kongou's Amazing When She Strips by KASAMA Sanshirou & UESUGI Hikaru
3. Ane Training  by TAGUCHI Kenji
4. Mizusawa Senpai Is Too Defenseless...!!  by Brocco Lee/Broccoli
5. Yacchan Wants to Confess by Toudori
6. Hard Girlfriend and Soft Girlfriend by YANO Toshinori
7. A Huge Roller Strategy by James HOTATE
